2
00:01:35,030 --> 00:01:37,870
(The Sixteenth Strategy Stealing on the Sly)

3
00:01:44,580 --> 00:01:45,850
In a day or two, General Li Yan

4
00:01:46,550 --> 00:01:47,550
will go to Chengdu again

5
00:01:48,820 --> 00:01:50,180
to report on the details of Zhulong's Case.

6
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:52,450
Before he comes back,

7
00:01:53,090 --> 00:01:54,620
go find a good house

8
00:01:56,020 --> 00:01:57,100
in a secluded place.

9
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:58,710
Looks like

10
00:01:59,110 --> 00:02:01,110
he actually likes Miss Liu.

11
00:02:03,460 --> 00:02:04,460
A prostitute of talent like her

12
00:02:04,690 --> 00:02:06,940
often visits General Li's house

13
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:08,289
and this would create a bad impression.

14
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:09,759
It's a mere trifle.

15
00:02:10,460 --> 00:02:12,780
I'll satisfy General Li Yan.

16
00:02:14,210 --> 00:02:15,720
You're now in charge of the scribe room.

17
00:02:17,260 --> 00:02:18,170
You can't do a good job

18
00:02:18,390 --> 00:02:19,990
unless you consider everything

19
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:21,200
before your superior.

20
00:02:22,910 --> 00:02:24,230
I get it, Feng Ying.

21
00:02:26,090 --> 00:02:29,060
Gao Tangbing's case

22
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:30,930
must have been disadvantageous to you, right?

23
00:02:32,700 --> 00:02:34,500
At last, you realized it.

24
00:02:35,500 --> 00:02:36,420
His case is more than disadvantageous.

25
00:02:37,670 --> 00:02:38,880
Can there be future trouble?

26
00:02:39,100 --> 00:02:41,670
A chief in the Intelligence Analysis Department turned out to be a Wei spy.

27
00:02:43,460 --> 00:02:44,420
Think about it.

28
00:02:45,829 --> 00:02:47,790
It’s a horrible case for Siwencao Intelligence.

29
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:48,460
Got it?

30
00:02:48,480 --> 00:02:49,730
I thought about it.

31
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:51,720
But you're not to blame.

32
00:02:52,070 --> 00:02:54,220
Gao Tangbing kept telling me

33
00:02:54,500 --> 00:02:56,430
that the clerk couldn't be perspicacious about everything,

34
00:02:56,579 --> 00:02:59,410
no matter who he was.

35
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,220
Besides, in Siwencao Intelligence,

36
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,400
Yang Yi used to be your immediate superior.

37
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,860
It can't be your turn to take the blame.

38
00:03:06,390 --> 00:03:07,660
Chief Yang Yi

39
00:03:08,070 --> 00:03:09,300
has been demoted to a plebeian.

40
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,970
If I don't take the blame,

41
00:03:12,340 --> 00:03:13,060
who else will?

42
00:03:14,820 --> 00:03:17,290
For the sake of your relationship with General Li Yan,

43
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:18,610
he will not stump you.

44
00:03:20,540 --> 00:03:22,410
It's so naive of you.

45
00:03:22,870 --> 00:03:24,390
Relations aren't helpful to us.

46
00:03:25,780 --> 00:03:27,140
Everything is decided by interests.

47
00:03:29,150 --> 00:03:31,150
Your superior will not defend you

48
00:03:31,170 --> 00:03:32,450
or keep you safe

49
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,160
unless you share the same interests with him, got it?

50
00:03:36,630 --> 00:03:37,990
Yes, got it.

51
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:51,540
Thank you.

52
00:04:05,630 --> 00:04:11,210
(Prime Minister’s Mansion in Chengdu, the Shu State)

53
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,770
Prime Minister invited you to a discussion.

54
00:04:39,180 --> 00:04:39,730
Come, please.

55
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,870
Don't stand on ceremony, everybody.

56
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:04,850
Today, you've been invited

57
00:05:04,850 --> 00:05:06,740
for another discussion on the Northern Expedition.

58
00:05:06,860 --> 00:05:07,510
Prime Minister,

59
00:05:07,540 --> 00:05:09,100
I don't agree on the Northern Expedition.

60
00:05:11,910 --> 00:05:13,270
Last night, I observed the sky.

61
00:05:13,550 --> 00:05:15,030
The North was flourishing

62
00:05:15,530 --> 00:05:16,500
and the stars were brilliant.

63
00:05:16,500 --> 00:05:16,720
(Qiao Zhou, the Grand Astrologer of Shu)
and the stars were brilliant.

64
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:17,130
(Qiao Zhou, the Grand Astrologer of Shu)

65
00:05:17,130 --> 00:05:18,100
We shouldn't attack the North.
(Qiao Zhou, the Grand Astrologer of Shu)

66
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:19,420
(Qiao Zhou, the Grand Astrologer of Shu)

67
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,010
Prime Minister, you're conversant with astronomy.
(Qiao Zhou, the Grand Astrologer of Shu)

68
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:23,210
Why must you go against it?

69
00:05:25,340 --> 00:05:26,580
Astronomy always changes.

70
00:05:26,610 --> 00:05:27,520
We mustn't be narrow-minded.

71
00:05:27,640 --> 00:05:29,090
I hold the same old view.

72
00:05:29,710 --> 00:05:31,750
Prime Minister, if you start the Northern Expedition again,

73
00:05:32,290 --> 00:05:34,780
I will lead five thousand picked soldiers to start from Baozhong County

74
00:05:34,870 --> 00:05:37,590
and go north along Ziwu Valley in the east of Qinling Mountains.

75
00:05:38,659 --> 00:05:40,700
In less than ten days, we'll arrive in Chang'an.

76
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:42,860
Upon seeing our sudden arrival,

77
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:45,240
the Wei Army will abandon the city and move towards Dige Town in the west.

78
00:05:45,950 --> 00:05:47,870
Then you can lead a large force there

79
00:05:47,900 --> 00:05:48,810
through Xiegu Valley.

80
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:51,420
In this way, we will conquer

81
00:05:51,890 --> 00:05:52,970
the west of Xianyang.

82
00:05:54,690 --> 00:05:55,860
This plan is way too rash.

83
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:57,970
Wei Yan,

84
00:05:58,350 --> 00:05:59,460
are you mocking the Wei State

85
00:05:59,770 --> 00:06:01,210
for having no talented generals?

86
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:04,610
If an ingenious Wei army lies in ambush

87
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,420
somewhere secluded on the mountain

88
00:06:07,110 --> 00:06:08,150
and cuts you off,

89
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,240
you can easily break into Ziwu Valley, but hardly leave there.

90
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,390
You'll then lose all your soldiers.

91
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:14,080
Prime Minister,

92
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:17,500
I don’t worry about military affairs.

93
00:06:19,060 --> 00:06:21,670
You failed the Northern Expedition last time.

94
00:06:22,800 --> 00:06:25,200
Even though you conquered southern barbarians,

95
00:06:25,340 --> 00:06:26,680
considerable national strength was depleted.

96
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,210
(Jiang Wan, Prime Minister’s Adjutant of Shu)
