00:06:35,620 --> 00:06:36,500
Go on.

103
00:06:38,550 --> 00:06:39,630
Since the late emperor passed away,

104
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,430
you've been holding military power and handling national affairs.

105
00:06:42,659 --> 00:06:44,409
The present emperor has misgivings about you.

106
00:06:45,500 --> 00:06:48,110
In the court, noble clans

107
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:50,650
from Jingzhou and Yizhou make things difficult for you.

108
00:06:51,220 --> 00:06:52,180
General Li Yan

109
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:55,159
strongly advocates the southern campaign against the Wu State

110
00:06:55,190 --> 00:06:56,630
to recover the lost territory of Jingzhou.

111
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:59,570
His strategic direction is totally opposed.

112
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:02,430
If you propose the Northern Expedition again,

113
00:07:02,460 --> 00:07:03,300
I'm afraid

114
00:07:03,790 --> 00:07:05,350
you can hardly have a perfect plan.

115
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:30,740
Somebody!

116
00:07:34,130 --> 00:07:35,490
What do you want, sir?

117
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,080
Has Prime Minister ended the discussion?

118
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,240
Not yet. It'll still take a long while.

119
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,790
I hold a different view

120
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:55,120
from Jiang Wan.

121
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:57,420
It is time to unite with the Wu State

122
00:07:58,050 --> 00:07:59,460
to fight against the Wei State.

123
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,830
The late emperor occupied Xichuan

124
00:08:03,400 --> 00:08:04,650
and ruled one-third of the whole country,

125
00:08:04,650 --> 00:08:05,220
(Deng Zhi, General of Expedition of Shu)
