129
00:08:10,230 --> 00:08:12,140
So, the prosperity of talents

130
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:14,260
can be the very foundation of a state.

131
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:17,300
Now, three states rule the whole country.

132
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:19,150
Nearly all places are in peace.

133
00:08:19,490 --> 00:08:22,490
But with talents and material resources in Xichuan alone,

134
00:08:22,690 --> 00:08:25,050
we aren't strong enough to fight against Wei or Wu for mastery.

135
00:08:26,790 --> 00:08:30,190
Our state is like sailing against the current.

136
00:08:31,010 --> 00:08:33,380
If we don't conquer the Central Plains through the Northern Expedition,

137
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:37,429
we'll certainly crumble in three or five years.

138
00:08:37,990 --> 00:08:39,620
What Deng Zhi just said is exactly my point.

139
00:08:40,570 --> 00:08:41,330
In this world,

140
00:08:41,950 --> 00:08:43,669
there's no such thing as perfection.

141
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:47,260
The Wei State is strong and our state is weak.

142
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,420
If things go on like this,

143
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:51,610
we will decline while they will prosper.

144
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:52,670
In this way,

145
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:53,900
our state built by the late emperor

146
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,740
will be annexed by the Wei State sooner or later!

147
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,360
But if we fight them now,

148
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,680
we may stand a chance to win.

149
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:05,420
The late emperor

150
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,060
visited me three times

151
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,760
and entrusted his son to me.

152
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,350
Even though the future is perilous,

153
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:16,570
I will not shrink from any sacrifice.

154
00:09:19,430 --> 00:09:22,470
Prime Minister, you have a long-term perspective

155
00:09:22,890 --> 00:09:24,970
and you consider more than us.

156
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,670
A couple of days ago,

157
00:09:30,230 --> 00:09:32,270
I stationed troops in Ji Valley of Mount Qi.

158
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:36,140
We had more soldiers and weapons

159
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:37,980
than the Wei Army.

160
00:09:39,290 --> 00:09:41,290
Instead of defeating them, we were defeated.

161
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:44,640
The problem doesn't lie in the number of soldiers

162
00:09:44,670 --> 00:09:46,620
or the national power,

163
00:09:48,470 --> 00:09:50,620
but the commander's decisions.

164
00:09:53,050 --> 00:09:53,840
Everybody,

165
00:09:56,380 --> 00:09:58,060
you must learn a lesson from it.

166
00:09:58,240 --> 00:09:59,360
Aye.

