170
00:10:08,280 --> 00:10:08,340
propose the Northern Expedition again.
(Li Yan's Camp in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

171
00:10:08,340 --> 00:10:10,130
propose the Northern Expedition again.

172
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,560
I didn't expect him

173
00:10:13,040 --> 00:10:14,480
to be so stubborn.

174
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:18,960
Zhulong's Case has been cracked.

175
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,990
Maybe Zhuge Liang believes

176
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:24,410
that there's no future trouble

177
00:10:25,540 --> 00:10:26,740
and we can fight the Wei State

178
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,620
without concern.

179
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:31,300
General,

180
00:10:32,000 --> 00:10:33,360
what's the attitude of His Majesty?

181
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:36,080
I can hardly tell.

182
00:10:38,330 --> 00:10:39,520
His Majesty

183
00:10:40,050 --> 00:10:42,010
has something on his mind, too.

184
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:45,100
Will they make an issue

185
00:10:45,980 --> 00:10:47,700
of Zhulong's Case?

186
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:49,630
Perhaps.

187
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:53,290
Feng Ying has a new backer.

188
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:55,090
They're going to deal with him.

189
00:10:56,490 --> 00:10:58,010
Gao Tangbing is a Wei spy.

190
00:10:58,220 --> 00:10:59,090
Feng Ying

191
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:00,940
must be culpable.

192
00:11:02,590 --> 00:11:03,360
Shall we defend Feng Ying?

193
00:11:06,060 --> 00:11:06,900
Let me think about it.

194
00:11:09,060 --> 00:11:09,820
General,

195
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,680
Chen Gong of Siwencao Intelligence asked to see you.

196
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:17,220
Get him in.

197
00:11:22,850 --> 00:11:24,060
I, Chen Gong, am here.

198
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,440
Greetings, General.

199
00:11:32,770 --> 00:11:33,580
You may rise.

200
00:11:36,310 --> 00:11:38,270
You're now a hero of our state

201
00:11:38,300 --> 00:11:39,580
who is famous all around the country.

202
00:11:39,890 --> 00:11:42,050
You no longer need to be as courteous as before.

203
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,300
You used to be my teacher

204
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:44,770
and you're always like my father.

205
00:11:45,260 --> 00:11:46,720
I was so busy working in the Agency

206
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:50,160
that I didn’t visit you in time.

207
00:11:50,620 --> 00:11:51,590
I feel quite guilty.

208
00:11:51,620 --> 00:11:52,880
Please forgive me.

209
00:11:55,300 --> 00:11:56,170
I know

210
00:11:56,810 --> 00:11:58,610
what happened to you.

211
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:00,710
I’m sorry for your loss.

212
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:04,610
Thank you, sir.

213
00:12:10,030 --> 00:12:10,750
Come on.

214
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,560
I wondered

215
00:12:12,750 --> 00:12:14,230
why I had never heard from you

216
00:12:14,660 --> 00:12:17,310
since we parted a few years ago.

217
00:12:17,430 --> 00:12:18,200
It turns out

218
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:22,260
that you’ve been working for Siwencao Intelligence.

219
00:12:22,690 --> 00:12:24,960
Sorry, I was so young and arrogant

220
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:27,030
that I didn't live up to your cultivation.

221
00:12:27,500 --> 00:12:28,260
Be seated.

222
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:30,540
Come on.

223
00:12:34,380 --> 00:12:35,330
Chen Gong,

224
00:12:36,690 --> 00:12:37,770
you're wrong about it.

225
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,890
Everyone has his own ambition.

226
00:12:40,110 --> 00:12:41,860
If you served as an official,

227
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:43,130
you may not

228
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:44,660
be patient enough.

229
00:12:47,730 --> 00:12:48,620
Sir,

230
00:12:49,030 --> 00:12:50,420
you can really read my mind.

231
00:12:50,580 --> 00:12:51,700
I'm glad to have you back.

232
00:12:52,460 --> 00:12:54,470
Siwencao Intelligence is short of men.

233
00:12:54,500 --> 00:12:55,900
I'm rather embattled.

234
00:12:56,300 --> 00:12:57,370
If you want me to do anything,

235
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:59,180
I dare not decline it.

236
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,700
Work in the Agency is complicated.

237
00:13:04,460 --> 00:13:05,780
You must be prepared.

238
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:10,390
Zhulong's Case has been cracked.

239
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:14,180
But Gao Tangbing was a chief of the Intelligence Analysis Department for a long time.

240
00:13:14,700 --> 00:13:15,890
We can't be sure

241
00:13:17,140 --> 00:13:20,220
if there were more hidden Wei spies.

242
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,440
Don't worry, sir.

243
00:13:23,350 --> 00:13:24,500
Now that I'm back,

244
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,640
I'll get to the bottom of this case.

245
00:13:27,250 --> 00:13:27,860
And I will

246
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:29,110
let go of no one.

247
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:31,250
Good. Very good.

248
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,150
I told Feng Ying

249
00:13:33,620 --> 00:13:35,900
that you would take the place of Li Miao.

250
00:13:35,930 --> 00:13:38,960
He may not be able to manage it alone.

251
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,580
Thank you, sir.

252
00:13:58,010 --> 00:13:59,160
At the morning court,

253
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:00,720
there will be disputes.

254
00:14:01,350 --> 00:14:03,900
General Li Yan just cracked Zhulong's Case.

255
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:07,630
He won't easily agree on the Northern Expedition, Prime Minister.

256
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:10,290
It’s up to His Majesty to make a decision.

257
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:12,460
This is exactly what worries me.

258
00:14:15,210 --> 00:14:16,720
Man proposes, God disposes.

259
00:14:18,140 --> 00:14:19,230
Don't guess too much.

260
00:14:20,520 --> 00:14:21,130
Aye.

261
00:14:24,890 --> 00:14:26,220
What else do you want to say?

262
00:14:29,200 --> 00:14:31,600
Chief Yang Yi was at fault.

263
00:14:32,410 --> 00:14:35,010
But he has been industrious for years.

264
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:37,330
And he’s very loyal to you.

265
00:14:42,940 --> 00:14:43,660
Are you defending him?

266
00:14:44,140 --> 00:14:44,750
Yes.

267
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:47,330
Chief Yang is very capable.

268
00:14:47,900 --> 00:14:50,660
When we fight enemies, it will be idle if we leave him unused.

269
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:57,010
We'll do it your way.

270
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:58,510
Make him work.

271
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:13,760
Zhuge Liang wants to hold a morning court

272
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:17,370
because he will discuss something in front of His Majesty.

273
00:15:18,250 --> 00:15:19,340
Wait until I'm back.

274
00:15:20,330 --> 00:15:21,300
After I'm back,

275
00:15:21,980 --> 00:15:24,150
let's figure out the plan.

276
00:15:24,730 --> 00:15:26,810
Wasn’t the morning court just held?

277
00:15:26,980 --> 00:15:28,460
Why will it be held again so soon?

278
00:15:29,230 --> 00:15:30,550
Zhuge Liang suddenly asked for it,

279
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:33,270
proposing a discussion on the second Northern Expedition.

280
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:36,550
Chen Gong,

281
00:15:37,360 --> 00:15:38,640
let me quiz you.

282
00:15:39,740 --> 00:15:40,860
The Northern Expedition...

283
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:42,620
I mean the second Northern Expedition.

284
00:15:43,470 --> 00:15:44,380
What do you think

285
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,840
of it?

286
00:15:47,230 --> 00:15:49,030
If Prime Minister insists on the Northern Expedition,

287
00:15:49,060 --> 00:15:50,180
why don't you

288
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:52,100
make a concession?

289
00:15:54,660 --> 00:15:55,980
This is a strange thing

290
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:58,560
to hear.

291
00:15:59,950 --> 00:16:01,860
Don't dream it. Be it.

292
00:16:02,670 --> 00:16:04,590
Now that Prime Minister is so stubborn,

293
00:16:04,940 --> 00:16:06,950
he will bring misery on himself.

294
00:16:07,830 --> 00:16:08,910
What makes you think so?

295
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:11,560
Do you still remember the testamentary edict of the late emperor?

296
00:16:12,020 --> 00:16:13,220
Yes, of course.

297
00:16:14,100 --> 00:16:15,250
The late emperor

298
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:17,250
said to Zhuge Liang,

299
00:16:18,230 --> 00:16:21,310
"You're ten times cleverer than Cao Pi.

300
00:16:21,780 --> 00:16:23,900
Assist my son if you think he's not too bad.

301
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,400
If he's too bad,

302
00:16:25,650 --> 00:16:27,490
take his place."

303
00:16:29,350 --> 00:16:30,280
The late emperor

304
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:32,850
thought highly

305
00:16:33,420 --> 00:16:35,030
of Zhuge Liang.

306
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:37,630
He even asked His Majesty

307
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:40,370
to call Zhuge Liang Godfather.

308
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:43,310
Zhuge Liang enjoys a glorious life.

309
00:16:43,910 --> 00:16:45,540
"Take his place."

310
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:47,390
His Majesty has a reason to kill him.

311
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:54,330
Chen Gong,

312
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:58,140
you've improved a lot over the years.

313
00:16:59,700 --> 00:17:01,100
You're back right in time.

314
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,750
You'll be my great helper.

315
00:17:02,960 --> 00:17:03,760
Sir,

316
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:04,960
you flatter me.

317
00:17:06,300 --> 00:17:07,060
Off you go.

318
00:17:08,250 --> 00:17:09,099
I'll take my leave, sir.

319
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,589
(Siwencao Intelligence in Nanzheng County, the Shu State)

320
00:17:28,470 --> 00:17:30,080
Li Miao used that tea table, didn't he?

321
00:17:30,100 --> 00:17:31,210
Why is it still there?

322
00:17:32,340 --> 00:17:34,180
We asked Clerk Chen about it

323
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:35,390
and he said it was okay.

324
00:17:35,960 --> 00:17:37,490
No way. Take it away.

325
00:17:37,840 --> 00:17:38,310
Aye.

326
00:17:38,410 --> 00:17:39,740
Why bother wiping the screen?

327
00:17:40,190 --> 00:17:41,830
Just move it away.

328
00:17:42,140 --> 00:17:42,740
Aye.

329
00:17:42,900 --> 00:17:43,790
You know what?

330
00:17:43,820 --> 00:17:45,380
Not even a single thing that Li Miao used

331
00:17:46,110 --> 00:17:48,020
can be kept in this room.

332
00:17:58,470 --> 00:17:59,230
Be careful, boss.

333
00:18:11,720 --> 00:18:12,760
Xun Xu,

334
00:18:13,900 --> 00:18:15,100
you've come at last.

335
00:18:17,030 --> 00:18:18,620
You were quite patient.

336
00:18:24,650 --> 00:18:26,330
What happened to you?

337
00:18:27,730 --> 00:18:29,770
To catch you,

338
00:18:30,650 --> 00:18:32,440
I had to pay some price.

339
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:38,060
You were tortured?

340
00:19:00,490 --> 00:19:02,100
It never occurred to me

341
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,070
that you and Baidi

342
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:07,900
put on a good play.

343
00:19:11,840 --> 00:19:12,850
Good play?

344
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:17,340
The play was fake,

345
00:19:18,630 --> 00:19:19,860
but we indeed paid the price.

346
00:19:21,780 --> 00:19:22,460
Xun Xu,

347
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,990
I've never thought

348
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:27,080
about getting you involved.

349
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,780
You reminded Huang Yu,

350
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,880
so that our spy died.

351
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:32,910
You're guilty!

352
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:34,630
No spy

353
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:36,260
can ever control his own life.

354
00:19:36,630 --> 00:19:37,760
You just lost a spy.

355
00:19:37,860 --> 00:19:39,340
Do you know who she is?

356
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:45,830
She's Di Yue.

357
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:47,870
My cousin

358
00:19:49,130 --> 00:19:50,820
and Baidi's wife.

359
00:20:02,040 --> 00:20:02,800
Xun Xu,

360
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:05,390
you and I are insiders.

361
00:20:06,520 --> 00:20:08,050
If we didn’t work for different states,

362
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:12,030
we would still be good buddies.

363
00:20:13,280 --> 00:20:13,990
Yeah.

364
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:18,100
My cousin died a tragic death.

365
00:20:19,610 --> 00:20:21,180
I'm paralyzed from the waist down.

366
00:20:22,310 --> 00:20:25,360
It's all because of you, my good buddy!

367
00:20:30,270 --> 00:20:31,360
If you think so,

368
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,000
I have nothing to say.

369
00:20:51,700 --> 00:20:53,330
I'd like to verify something.

370
00:20:55,020 --> 00:20:59,420
You told Huang Yu the changing sequence of the night patrol passwords

371
00:21:00,090 --> 00:21:01,610
of the Military Technology Department, right?

372
00:21:06,950 --> 00:21:07,510
Yes.

373
00:21:27,970 --> 00:21:28,690
Clerk Chen,

374
00:21:30,380 --> 00:21:32,190
your room has been cleaned up.

375
00:21:32,260 --> 00:21:34,140
Everything is replaced.

376
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:38,220
Before the official appointment is issued,

377
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:39,540
you'd better not

378
00:21:40,250 --> 00:21:41,450
call me Clerk Chen yet.

379
00:21:43,130 --> 00:21:44,620
Isn't it only a matter of time?

380
00:21:44,640 --> 00:21:45,400
Besides,

381
00:21:45,430 --> 00:21:46,220
if you have nowhere to live

382
00:21:46,240 --> 00:21:47,690
when you're back in Siwencao Intelligence,

383
00:21:47,720 --> 00:21:48,720
it would be ridiculous.

384
00:21:49,410 --> 00:21:50,360
Thank you, Chief Sun.

385
00:21:50,910 --> 00:21:52,190
You're welcome, Clerk Chen.

386
00:21:52,340 --> 00:21:53,420
You deserve it.

387
00:21:55,350 --> 00:21:56,550
I have something to tell Feng Ying.

388
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:58,940
I'll check my room later.

389
00:21:58,970 --> 00:22:00,380
Okay. Do whatever you want.

390
00:22:04,910 --> 00:22:06,380
Don't worry about such problems.

391
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:09,040
Just take office.

392
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:12,450
Clerk Feng,

393
00:22:13,310 --> 00:22:15,030
you're my guide in Siwencao Intelligence.

394
00:22:16,430 --> 00:22:17,560
But I'm not capable enough

395
00:22:17,590 --> 00:22:19,220
to be the chief clerk.

396
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:22,460
General Li Yan told me to take care of you.

397
00:22:23,090 --> 00:22:23,890
Besides,

398
00:22:26,010 --> 00:22:27,690
being the Chief Clerk

399
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:29,540
may only be a transition for you.

400
00:22:32,990 --> 00:22:33,600
Clerk Feng,

401
00:22:34,790 --> 00:22:36,310
what does that mean?

402
00:22:36,570 --> 00:22:37,490
I don't really understand.

403
00:22:41,730 --> 00:22:43,130
Gao Tangbing turned out to be a spy.

404
00:22:44,430 --> 00:22:46,110
It damaged the foundation of Siwencao Intelligence.

405
00:22:46,800 --> 00:22:49,680
Someone has to take the blame.

406
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:54,230
But Clerk Feng,

407
00:22:54,920 --> 00:22:56,600
you've been making painstaking efforts and racking your brains

408
00:22:56,630 --> 00:22:57,380
for Siwencao Intelligence.

409
00:22:58,170 --> 00:22:59,210
In the past dozen years,

410
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:00,910
you've performed outstanding service.

411
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:03,670
Even if the court wants to investigate Zhulong's Case,

412
00:23:03,890 --> 00:23:05,560
you will only have to offset your guilt.

413
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:06,880
I don't think you'll be dismissed.

414
00:23:08,010 --> 00:23:08,780
Chen Gong,

415
00:23:10,220 --> 00:23:11,130
you're just back

416
00:23:12,340 --> 00:23:14,220
and you don't understand

417
00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:16,580
how official circles work.

418
00:23:18,330 --> 00:23:19,050
Clerk Feng,

419
00:23:20,100 --> 00:23:22,580
do you misunderstand that I have designs on your post?

420
00:23:22,600 --> 00:23:23,560
No, Chen Gong.

421
00:23:24,490 --> 00:23:25,450
It's not that I misunderstand you.

422
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:28,000
I say this just in case.

423
00:23:32,140 --> 00:23:33,220
Anyway,

424
00:23:34,810 --> 00:23:36,060
I made lifelong efforts

425
00:23:37,340 --> 00:23:39,420
on Siwencao Intelligence.

426
00:23:39,610 --> 00:23:41,730
If I no longer work in the Agency,

427
00:23:42,220 --> 00:23:44,050
I want a capable insider

428
00:23:44,260 --> 00:23:45,770
to take my place

429
00:23:46,410 --> 00:23:47,810
so that

430
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:50,030
the intelligence agency of our state

431
00:23:50,530 --> 00:23:51,810
will not be ruined completely.

432
00:23:58,080 --> 00:23:58,840
You...

433
00:23:59,630 --> 00:24:00,580
You're different from Li Miao.

434
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,530
You can easily understand

435
00:24:03,940 --> 00:24:05,110
the stuff of Siwencao Intelligence.

436
00:24:10,410 --> 00:24:14,810
(Chen Gong, the Chief Clerk)

437
00:24:19,340 --> 00:24:20,100
Clerk Feng,

438
00:24:20,630 --> 00:24:21,580
if you want me to do anything,

439
00:24:22,140 --> 00:24:23,510
feel free to tell me.

440
00:24:27,050 --> 00:24:28,140
Let me make a long story short.

441
00:24:28,770 --> 00:24:30,140
Wuxian Sect was destroyed.

442
00:24:30,760 --> 00:24:31,640
Zhulong was caught.

443
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:32,890
We shall leave the aftermath work

444
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,330
to the Internal Affairs Department.

445
00:24:34,540 --> 00:24:35,500
However,

446
00:24:36,460 --> 00:24:38,140
we must keep the long-term perspective.

447
00:24:38,250 --> 00:24:39,170
I quite agree.

448
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:41,600
We shouldn't always let Wei spies

449
00:24:42,350 --> 00:24:44,470
lead us by the nose.

450
00:24:44,580 --> 00:24:45,470
That's exactly my point.

451
00:24:46,540 --> 00:24:47,470
We must strike back.

452
00:24:48,360 --> 00:24:49,680
We must have our own plans.

453
00:24:51,190 --> 00:24:52,310
But before that,

454
00:24:53,290 --> 00:24:54,560
we should make clear our targets.

455
00:24:55,210 --> 00:24:56,100
Two targets.

456
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,880
First, against our enemy,

457
00:24:58,180 --> 00:24:58,970
the Wei State.

458
00:24:59,970 --> 00:25:01,300
Second, domestic problems.

459
00:25:02,020 --> 00:25:02,660
Domestic problems?

460
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:06,500
Xun Xu,

461
00:25:07,210 --> 00:25:08,740
for your sake,

462
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,430
I'll speak without reserve.

463
00:25:11,460 --> 00:25:13,620
Baidi's code-cracking plates were strictly defended.

464
00:25:14,940 --> 00:25:16,530
How did you get the plates?

465
00:25:17,350 --> 00:25:18,220
From Sun Ling.

466
00:25:19,650 --> 00:25:20,820
You know him.

467
00:25:21,220 --> 00:25:22,220
He’s got many faults.

468
00:25:23,270 --> 00:25:24,740
It wasn’t hard

469
00:25:25,620 --> 00:25:26,700
to steal something from him.

470
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,390
Be specific.

471
00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:32,030
Specific?

472
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:37,040
It happened quite a long time ago.

473
00:25:37,460 --> 00:25:38,750
I have to think carefully

474
00:25:40,770 --> 00:25:42,090
about the specific conditions.

475
00:25:45,060 --> 00:25:46,350
About one year ago,

476
00:25:46,810 --> 00:25:47,900
Baidi's code-cracking plates

477
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:49,580
were kept

478
00:25:49,890 --> 00:25:51,500
by Sun Ling.

479
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:54,710
Clerk Feng contacted Baidi

480
00:25:54,750 --> 00:25:55,990
very secretly.

481
00:25:56,550 --> 00:25:58,070
The plates were strictly guarded

482
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:59,490
by twelve White-feather Warriors

483
00:25:59,870 --> 00:26:02,080
every time they were transferred.

484
00:26:02,530 --> 00:26:04,180
I couldn't steal them at all.

485
00:26:04,580 --> 00:26:06,700
Sun Ling was my chance.

486
00:26:07,460 --> 00:26:10,060
I made the same box as his.

487
00:26:10,430 --> 00:26:11,960
Every time before he traveled,

488
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:14,030
I exchanged the boxes.

489
00:26:14,930 --> 00:26:17,050
Sun Ling never realized it.

490
00:26:20,030 --> 00:26:21,420
At the destination,

491
00:26:21,820 --> 00:26:24,540
I exchanged the boxes again.

492
00:26:25,830 --> 00:26:26,830
By then,

493
00:26:27,190 --> 00:26:28,510
I already got the plates.

494
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:33,590
The whole process was perfect.

495
00:26:34,370 --> 00:26:35,480
Do you have any liaisons?

496
00:26:36,090 --> 00:26:39,090
I was a chief in the Intelligence Analysis Department.

497
00:26:40,320 --> 00:26:41,520
It was hard for a spy

498
00:26:41,550 --> 00:26:43,390
of the Military Intelligence Agency to have such a high position.

499
00:26:43,610 --> 00:26:44,800
I was very cautious.

500
00:26:45,540 --> 00:26:46,990
I always took independent action.

501
00:26:47,840 --> 00:26:49,310
As an insider, you must be aware

502
00:26:49,510 --> 00:26:50,900
that more persons involved

503
00:26:51,270 --> 00:26:53,460
will lead to more danger of exposure, right?

504
00:26:54,310 --> 00:26:55,710
How did you contact the Wei Army?

505
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:57,390
You're aware of that, too.

506
00:26:58,440 --> 00:26:59,760
I made use of the communication channel

507
00:27:00,050 --> 00:27:01,810
of Siwencao Intelligence.

508
00:27:02,240 --> 00:27:05,470
I fabricated a spy named Chidi

509
00:27:06,200 --> 00:27:08,970
who was actually used

510
00:27:08,990 --> 00:27:10,110
to transmit intel for my own state.

511
00:27:10,830 --> 00:27:12,110
It was a loophole

512
00:27:12,650 --> 00:27:15,500
in your defense.

513
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:19,530
When did you know about Gu Zheng?

514
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,500
Didn't you just say

515
00:27:26,180 --> 00:27:27,340
you would speak without reserve?

516
00:27:30,340 --> 00:27:31,290
Tangbing,

517
00:27:32,120 --> 00:27:33,590
am I asking the crucial question?

518
00:27:38,610 --> 00:27:39,690
In this industry,

519
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,220
if you don't reply,

520
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,340
you'll suffer.

521
00:27:44,050 --> 00:27:45,280
You know it very well.

522
00:27:48,880 --> 00:27:49,920
How about another question?

523
00:27:50,560 --> 00:27:52,040
You know what I can do.

524
00:27:53,120 --> 00:27:55,120
As long as I find a crack,

525
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:58,310
I'll rip it open soon.

526
00:28:00,330 --> 00:28:01,450
Ask another question.

527
00:28:02,440 --> 00:28:03,330
Otherwise,

528
00:28:04,180 --> 00:28:06,220
this is where we have to stop.

529
00:28:08,190 --> 00:28:08,940
Fine.

530
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:11,680
You have a few moments.

531
00:28:12,120 --> 00:28:13,400
Think about it.

532
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:20,670
Wait.

533
00:28:30,730 --> 00:28:31,690
I'll speak, under two conditions.

534
00:28:33,160 --> 00:28:34,100
Go on.

535
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:38,100
I want the token granted by His Majesty

536
00:28:39,180 --> 00:28:40,830
to absolve me from all my sins.

537
00:28:41,510 --> 00:28:42,300
Then release me

538
00:28:42,860 --> 00:28:44,410
and no longer hunt me down.

539
00:28:50,290 --> 00:28:51,140
Xun Xu.

540
00:28:52,940 --> 00:28:53,830
Xun Xu!

541
00:29:02,300 --> 00:29:04,870
Prime Minister is convening the morning court again

542
00:29:05,230 --> 00:29:06,460
to discuss the second Northern Expedition.

543
00:29:08,260 --> 00:29:09,340
Siwencao Intelligence

544
00:29:09,840 --> 00:29:11,050
had a false intelligence case before.

545
00:29:11,860 --> 00:29:13,110
We mustn't repeat an error

546
00:29:13,340 --> 00:29:14,830
like Jieting's false intelligence case.

547
00:29:18,670 --> 00:29:20,070
I've been doing the fieldwork all year round.

548
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:22,750
I'm familiar with that.

549
00:29:23,830 --> 00:29:24,470
All right.

550
00:29:25,640 --> 00:29:27,080
I'll have you handle the Operations Department.

551
00:29:27,940 --> 00:29:29,490
I'll let Yin Ji know

552
00:29:30,050 --> 00:29:31,120
that he will be subordinate to you.

553
00:29:33,100 --> 00:29:34,060
In this way,

554
00:29:35,340 --> 00:29:36,510
even if I'm away,

555
00:29:36,900 --> 00:29:38,140
I'll be relieved

556
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:40,020
when you keep an eye on the fieldwork.

557
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:53,060
Clerk Chen.

558
00:30:14,000 --> 00:30:16,030
I'm Sun Ling. I ask to see you, Clerk Feng.

559
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:16,760
Come on in.

560
00:30:19,600 --> 00:30:21,030
Feng Ying, it’s me.

561
00:30:27,900 --> 00:30:28,940
Have you arranged everything for him?

562
00:30:29,640 --> 00:30:30,450
Yes.

563
00:30:31,170 --> 00:30:33,250
Everything Li Miao used has been replaced.

564
00:30:34,870 --> 00:30:36,190
If he wants you to do anything,

565
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:37,880
do it conscientiously for him.

566
00:30:38,780 --> 00:30:40,420
Chen Gong isn't like Li Miao.

567
00:30:41,190 --> 00:30:42,040
I will, of course.

568
00:30:42,330 --> 00:30:44,690
You instructed Chen Gong personally.

569
00:30:44,710 --> 00:30:45,630
He's one of us.

570
00:30:50,950 --> 00:30:54,200
Chen Gong used to be General Li Yan's student.

571
00:30:54,980 --> 00:30:55,980
They're close.

572
00:30:57,110 --> 00:30:58,320
Don't get it wrong.

573
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:03,820
So, Chen Gong isn't on our side?

574
00:31:06,350 --> 00:31:07,270
Don't overthink.

575
00:31:07,820 --> 00:31:09,180
Just do whatever you're asked.

576
00:31:09,470 --> 00:31:10,240
Got it?

577
00:31:10,300 --> 00:31:11,410
Yes, Feng Ying.

578
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:21,880
Sun Ling,

579
00:31:24,420 --> 00:31:25,940
if anything happens to me,

580
00:31:26,370 --> 00:31:27,570
I can no longer take care of you.

581
00:31:28,820 --> 00:31:29,580
Remember.

582
00:31:30,660 --> 00:31:31,860
Always be modest.

583
00:31:34,320 --> 00:31:35,040
Feng Ying,

584
00:31:35,850 --> 00:31:36,820
have you got any news

585
00:31:37,470 --> 00:31:38,510
from Chengdu?

586
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:41,570
Not yet.

587
00:31:43,590 --> 00:31:44,890
But previous preparations

588
00:31:45,670 --> 00:31:47,510
always lead to success

589
00:31:48,210 --> 00:31:50,210
