590
00:31:51,320 --> 00:31:53,530
Now that General Li Yan doesn't defend you,

591
00:31:54,130 --> 00:31:56,060
why do you still bother looking for a good house

592
00:31:56,080 --> 00:31:57,400
for him?

593
00:31:58,020 --> 00:31:59,820
Such a big favor will be wasted.

594
00:32:00,240 --> 00:32:01,480
It's even less beneficial than raising a dog.

595
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:03,020
Nonsense!

596
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:04,750
But Feng Ying,

597
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:07,110
this is the truth I'm telling.

598
00:32:09,870 --> 00:32:10,940
I'm not looking for a house

599
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,000
to defend my job,

600
00:32:14,010 --> 00:32:15,120
but to keep myself alive!

601
00:32:41,700 --> 00:32:54,460
(Ziyan House)

602
00:32:54,980 --> 00:32:56,550
Sir, which girl would you like to see?

603
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:59,230
There's a Miss Liu Ying here, right?

604
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:00,660
Yes, there is.

605
00:33:01,260 --> 00:33:03,340
But Miss Liu is the best girl here.

606
00:33:06,530 --> 00:33:07,000
Is the money enough?

607
00:33:13,860 --> 00:33:15,870
I'm Ying'er, Miss Liu's maid.

608
00:33:16,250 --> 00:33:17,290
Come this way, please.

609
00:33:17,320 --> 00:33:17,960
All right.

610
00:33:28,030 --> 00:33:29,620
Nice to meet you, Mister Chen.

611
00:33:30,090 --> 00:33:31,210
I wonder what you like.

612
00:33:33,470 --> 00:33:34,310
What can you do?

613
00:33:35,670 --> 00:33:38,030
I can play some musical instruments.

614
00:33:40,410 --> 00:33:41,890
If you don’t like that,

615
00:33:42,520 --> 00:33:44,640
I can also sing a song for you

616
