I'm a bit of a boor and not interested in that.

618
00:33:50,920 --> 00:33:52,890
I guess it's your first time to visit us

619
00:33:53,070 --> 00:33:54,320
and you don't know the rules.

620
00:33:55,120 --> 00:33:56,040
In this place,

621
00:33:56,340 --> 00:33:57,530
we offer all kinds of entertainment.

622
00:33:58,100 --> 00:33:59,310
You just need to be patient.

623
00:34:18,230 --> 00:34:20,460
Though the tortoise lives long, it dies anyway.

624
00:34:21,570 --> 00:34:22,489
The serpent flies,

625
00:34:23,350 --> 00:34:24,300
