00:34:58,940 --> 00:35:01,060
The defense of Chencang County has been basically completed.

634
00:35:01,450 --> 00:35:03,130
A 3,000-soldier vanguard has arrived.

635
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:05,760
Another 2,000 soldiers are on their way.

636
00:35:06,050 --> 00:35:07,490
They'll be arriving in two days.

637
00:35:08,690 --> 00:35:11,300
I'm Guo Gang who's guilty. Greetings, Inspector Guo.

638
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,710
Let's call it a day.

639
00:35:15,740 --> 00:35:17,530
You may leave for some rest.

640
00:35:17,680 --> 00:35:18,610
Aye.

641
00:35:21,790 --> 00:35:23,150
Thank you, Inspector Guo.

642
00:35:30,570 --> 00:35:31,290
Guo Gang,

643
00:35:34,260 --> 00:35:36,620
I've been too busy

644
00:35:36,640 --> 00:35:37,680
to care about you lately.

645
00:35:38,760 --> 00:35:39,550
Uncle,

646
00:35:40,600 --> 00:35:42,930
I swear I didn't know that Chen Gong was Baidi.

647
00:35:42,950 --> 00:35:45,270
I also didn't know that Chen Gong was still alive.

648
00:35:45,460 --> 00:35:46,270
I'm sorry.

649
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,950
All right. Be seated first.

650
00:35:52,370 --> 00:35:54,560
You did something so reckless.

651
00:35:54,620 --> 00:35:57,100
But I wasn't surprised at all.

652
00:35:57,700 --> 00:35:58,630
It doesn't matter.

653
00:35:59,220 --> 00:36:00,700
Young men can make mistakes.

654
00:36:01,750 --> 00:36:02,670
You should learn a lesson from it.

655
00:36:05,980 --> 00:36:06,630
All right.

656
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:07,880
Go get packed

657
00:36:09,080 --> 00:36:10,480
and return to Tianshui.

658
00:36:18,610 --> 00:36:19,330
I...

659
00:36:20,580 --> 00:36:21,660
I haven't atoned for my mistake yet.

660
00:36:22,690 --> 00:36:24,090
How could I resume my post?

661
00:36:25,170 --> 00:36:27,680
Qingping Plan is in its last stage.

662
00:36:30,540 --> 00:36:32,980
Did we get the design of the crossbow?

663
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:37,900
The real secret of Qingping Plan

664
00:36:38,260 --> 00:36:39,700
doesn't aim to steal crossbow techniques,

665
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:44,820
but to plant our spy

666
00:36:45,540 --> 00:36:47,620
to the highest management level.

667
00:36:48,220 --> 00:36:48,980
Think about it.

668
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:50,700
If Zhulong

669
00:36:51,030 --> 00:36:52,430
can serve as a chief

670
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:53,780
in Siwencao Intelligence,

671
00:36:54,100 --> 00:36:55,030
then,

672
00:36:56,160 --> 00:36:58,240
we will lose no time in getting

673
00:36:58,610 --> 00:37:00,420
all the important military intel of Shu.

674
00:37:01,190 --> 00:37:04,230
This is how we can win wars.

675
00:37:05,980 --> 00:37:07,340
I still don't understand, Uncle.

676
00:37:08,100 --> 00:37:09,100
Gao Tangbing

677
00:37:10,330 --> 00:37:11,500
has been caught, hasn't he?

678
00:37:11,780 --> 00:37:13,020
Zhulong is only a code name.

679
00:37:13,910 --> 00:37:16,140
When Gao Tangbing was exposed,

680
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:18,080
he was no longer Zhulong.

681
00:37:19,030 --> 00:37:22,510
Instead, he would cover Zhulong.

682
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,160
Then, who is

683
00:37:35,670 --> 00:37:36,350
the new Zhulong?

684
00:37:42,140 --> 00:37:43,460
Play chess with me first.

685
00:37:53,350 --> 00:37:56,290
(Chengdu, the Shu State)

686
00:37:58,110 --> 00:38:00,670
(The Royal Palace)

687
00:38:05,300 --> 00:38:05,980
Greetings, sir.

688
00:38:06,580 --> 00:38:07,330
Greetings, Prime Minister.

689
00:39:56,000 --> 00:39:57,480
Prime Minister, after my father passed away,

690
00:39:57,780 --> 00:40:00,580
you went to the barren Lu River personally.

691
00:40:00,790 --> 00:40:03,280
After seven rounds of clashes, you conquered southern barbarians.

692
00:40:03,770 --> 00:40:05,450
You made unparalleled contributions.

693
00:40:06,790 --> 00:40:09,070
Now, neither the Wei nor Wu State

694
00:40:09,290 --> 00:40:11,410
wants to invade us.

695
00:40:11,730 --> 00:40:13,540
It's settled that three states rule the country.

696
00:40:14,700 --> 00:40:17,460
Prime Minister, why don't you just enjoy the peace?

697
00:40:18,140 --> 00:40:19,690
Why are you proposing the Northern Expedition again?

698
00:40:20,900 --> 00:40:21,730
Your Majesty,

699
00:40:22,260 --> 00:40:24,220
three states don't consort and we can't be satisfied with the sovereignty over a part of the country.

700
00:40:24,650 --> 00:40:25,210
Therefore,

701
00:40:25,970 --> 00:40:29,010
I propose to take the risk as the late emperor wished.

702
00:40:29,590 --> 00:40:32,710
Besieged with Wu and our state,

703
00:40:32,900 --> 00:40:34,900
the Wei Army is rather fatigued.

704
00:40:35,390 --> 00:40:37,140
It's time to make an attack.

705
00:40:37,850 --> 00:40:40,250
Prime Minister, if you're truly familiar with warcraft,

706
00:40:40,740 --> 00:40:44,090
why did you fail in Jieting?

707
00:40:45,120 --> 00:40:47,250
Cao Cao failed to defeat Chang Ba five times

708
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:48,720
and cross Chaohu Lake four times.

709
00:40:49,610 --> 00:40:51,250
He designated Li Fu, but Li Fu betrayed him.

710
00:40:51,270 --> 00:40:53,340
He then appointed Xiahou, but Xiahou was defeated and killed.

711
00:40:54,380 --> 00:40:57,330
Every time the late emperor spoke of Cao Cao,

712
00:40:57,360 --> 00:40:59,840
he praised him for commanding troops amazingly.

713
00:41:01,390 --> 00:41:04,620
Wars are complicated. No one can always win.

714
00:41:04,650 --> 00:41:05,940
If you say so,

715
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:08,430
we can fight the Wu State

716
00:41:08,980 --> 00:41:09,810
before the Wei State.

717
00:41:10,610 --> 00:41:15,000
Why must you insist on fighting the Wei State together with Wu?

718
00:41:16,110 --> 00:41:19,250
Besides, the late emperor was killed by the Wu Army.

719
00:41:19,970 --> 00:41:21,700
But you don't plan to take revenge

720
00:41:21,770 --> 00:41:22,770
or resume Jingzhou!

721
00:41:23,170 --> 00:41:26,330
How can you live up to the late emperor in heaven?

722
00:41:28,550 --> 00:41:30,020
Weak forces work together to fight a strong army.

723
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:31,250
It's what people do through the ages.

724
00:41:33,050 --> 00:41:35,450
Sun Quan has owned the Wu State through three generations.

725
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,320
His state has difficult terrain and people support him.

726
00:41:38,180 --> 00:41:39,540
Wise and virtuous officials work for him.

727
00:41:40,180 --> 00:41:42,170
We can ask him for help, instead of fighting him.

728
00:41:43,160 --> 00:41:44,050
What's worse,

729
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:46,980
I don't have a perfect plan for the expedition against Wu.

730
00:41:47,660 --> 00:41:50,150
The late emperor was capable enough. With millions of soldiers,

731
00:41:50,180 --> 00:41:52,620
he was still defeated by Lu Xun of Wu.

732
00:41:54,410 --> 00:41:56,130
If we break with the Wu State,

733
00:41:57,060 --> 00:41:59,580
the Wei Army will seize the chance and fight us.

734
00:42:00,580 --> 00:42:01,260
In this way,

735
00:42:02,250 --> 00:42:02,930
Your Majesty,

736
00:42:05,570 --> 00:42:07,690
you will lose the Hanzhong Region.

737
00:42:11,190 --> 00:42:11,790
Your Majesty,

738
00:42:13,530 --> 00:42:15,360
I've been in the Hanzhong Region for only a few years.

739
00:42:15,900 --> 00:42:18,060
During that, I lost more than 70 generals

740
00:42:19,100 --> 00:42:20,340
including Yang Qun, Ma Yu,

741
00:42:21,230 --> 00:42:24,150
Yan Zhi, Ding Li,

742
00:42:24,940 --> 00:42:27,130
Bai Shou, Liu He, and Deng Tong.

743
00:42:27,740 --> 00:42:28,980
I lost more than a thousand soldiers

744
00:42:29,410 --> 00:42:31,690
like commandos, elite soldiers, and cavalrymen.

745
00:42:32,330 --> 00:42:33,860
They were elite soldiers

746
00:42:33,880 --> 00:42:35,200
that had been gathered from different places over decades.

747
00:42:35,230 --> 00:42:37,140
They didn't only come from our state.

748
00:42:40,610 --> 00:42:41,520
In a few years,

749
00:42:43,860 --> 00:42:45,500
we will lose two-thirds of our troops.

750
00:42:45,620 --> 00:42:47,460
If we don't start a war against Wei now,

751
00:42:47,490 --> 00:42:48,170
our state

752
00:42:50,050 --> 00:42:50,800
will have

753
00:42:52,590 --> 00:42:54,560
no more advantage to fight our enemies!

754
00:43:00,220 --> 00:43:02,570
You made sense, Godfather.

755
00:43:09,600 --> 00:43:12,610
(Intelligence Agency in Longxi)
