00:43:18,140 --> 00:43:19,890
Absolutely typical.

758
00:43:20,140 --> 00:43:21,900
As Li Yan expected,

759
00:43:21,940 --> 00:43:24,450
Chen Gong paid a visit to him.

760
00:43:24,470 --> 00:43:26,230
After all, Chen Gong's father

761
00:43:26,260 --> 00:43:28,660
used to work for Li Yan.

762
00:43:28,680 --> 00:43:31,140
Li Yan has enough trust in Chen Gong.

763
00:43:31,170 --> 00:43:33,800
He made Chen Gong the Clerk

764
00:43:34,140 --> 00:43:36,900
and asked him to find out the remaining Wei spies

765
00:43:36,930 --> 00:43:38,900
in Siwencao Intelligence.

766
00:43:38,920 --> 00:43:40,520
It was superficial of me.

767
00:43:40,540 --> 00:43:42,860
I thought the case would be at an end

768
00:43:42,890 --> 00:43:44,850
after Gao Tangbing fell from power.

769
00:43:44,880 --> 00:43:47,510
Unexpectedly, Regional Inspector Guo Huai of Wei

770
00:43:47,540 --> 00:43:48,900
held back another trick.

771
00:43:48,930 --> 00:43:51,820
Chen Gong visited Miss Liu Ying

772
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:53,350
and exchanged code words with her.

773
00:43:53,380 --> 00:43:55,190
Guo Gang has also been kept in the dark

774
00:43:55,210 --> 00:43:57,120
even though he resumed his post.

775
00:43:57,150 --> 00:43:58,040
This is indeed

776
00:43:58,060 --> 00:43:59,820
a clever move.

777
00:43:59,850 --> 00:44:01,280
Xun Xu is quite impatient.

778
00:44:01,310 --> 00:44:03,800
Before he fully recovered, he interrogated Gao Tangbing.

779
00:44:03,820 --> 00:44:05,690
Don't get angry, Xun Xu.

780
00:44:05,720 --> 00:44:07,800
Come on, Gao Tangbing.

781
00:44:07,820 --> 00:44:09,220
We used to be colleagues, after all.

782
00:44:09,250 --> 00:44:10,780
Tell me about it.

783
00:44:10,800 --> 00:44:12,080
What faults do I have?

784
00:44:12,430 --> 00:44:13,750
Oh, boy.

785
00:44:13,780 --> 00:44:15,460
So, you replaced Baidi's code-cracking plates

786
00:44:15,500 --> 00:44:17,820
when I wasn't noticing.

787
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:20,460
This is so uncool that you did this!

788
00:44:20,460 --> 00:44:21,350
Besides,

789
00:44:21,380 --> 00:44:22,530
how did you have the cheek

790
00:44:22,560 --> 00:44:25,090
to point out the loophole in our defense?

791
00:44:25,110 --> 00:44:26,340
Before you confess everything,

792
00:44:26,370 --> 00:44:28,620
just stay in jail!

793
00:44:29,080 --> 00:44:30,510
When did Gao Tangbing

794
00:44:30,540 --> 00:44:32,550
know about Gu Zheng?

795
00:44:32,570 --> 00:44:35,900
Judging from Guo Huai's conversation with Guo Gang,

796
00:44:35,920 --> 00:44:37,400
there are new plots.

797
00:44:37,470 --> 00:44:39,820
Chen Gong's role is getting more complicated.

798
00:44:39,870 --> 00:44:42,140
Not only Li Yan thinks highly of him,

799
00:44:42,160 --> 00:44:43,770
but Feng Ying also

800
00:44:43,800 --> 00:44:47,240
wants him to take charge of Siwencao Intelligence.

